also, you should be able to re-create the ground truth set by calling `POST /api/v2/ground-truth-sets/app-run-set` with a request body like this
```{
  "name": "ground-truth-set-name",
  "job_id": "5a588702-c178-4792-b6d8-58bf68fd0062",
  "deployed_solution_id": "some-existing-app-version-id",
  "uuid": "generated-uuid",
  "workspace": "workspace-name",
}```
you can generate a uuid using a website like https://www.uuidgenerator.net/

@ayesha.ali can you verify the consequences of creating a ground truth set from a deployment run and a `deployed_solution_id` that doesn't match that deployment run? could this break anything?

